To run the hive code in Mr;
    set hive.execution.engine=mr;
    
To run the hive code in spark;
      set hive.execution.engine=spark;
      
Check the hive related variable;
     set ;
     
Check the variables related to hive, MR and hadoop;
    set -v;


 For update and delete queries use the below command for better results.
      set hive.optimize.sort.dynamic.partition=false 
